  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A statement from the Prime Minister on the discussions of the financial fund",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Mass Media Bandula Gunawardena said in Parliament today (4) that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe is scheduled to make a statement in Parliament tomorrow (5) regarding the progress of negotiations with the International Monetary Fund.",
        "The Minister said that several rounds of negotiations with the International Monetary Fund have been held so far and the Prime Minister will make a comment in this regard.",
        "Mr. Bandula Gunawardena mentioned this during the questions that require oral answers in the Parliament."
      ],
